# Frontend

The SEO Analyzer application uses Laravel Blade templates with modern JavaScript and CSS.

## Structure

- [resources/views](mdc:seo-analyzer/resources/views) - Contains Blade templates
- [resources/js](mdc:seo-analyzer/resources/js) - JavaScript code
- [resources/css](mdc:seo-analyzer/resources/css) - CSS styles
- [public](mdc:seo-analyzer/public) - Public assets

## Build System

The project uses Vite for asset compilation:
- [vite.config.js](mdc:seo-analyzer/vite.config.js) - Vite configuration

## Key Views

- Dashboard: [resources/views/dashboard.blade.php](mdc:seo-analyzer/resources/views/dashboard.blade.php)
- Content Editor: [resources/views/content](mdc:seo-analyzer/resources/views/content)
- SEO Results: [resources/views/seo-results](mdc:seo-analyzer/resources/views/seo-results)
- Layouts: [resources/views/layouts](mdc:seo-analyzer/resources/views/layouts)
